1
00:00:18,800 --> 00:00:20,600
Here, have a gift!

2
00:00:23,833 --> 00:00:26,066
[ISSEI] Dragon Shot!

3
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:27,400
Thanks, Issei!

4
00:00:28,500 --> 00:00:30,533
No prob. Everyone okay?

5
00:00:32,166 --> 00:00:33,633
[RIAS] This is too dangerous.

6
00:00:33,666 --> 00:00:34,533
Which is why I need you

7
00:00:34,566 --> 00:00:36,800
to please take care
of Gasper for me.

8
00:00:36,833 --> 00:00:38,533
[SIR ZECHS] All right.

9
00:00:38,566 --> 00:00:39,333
Can we kill them, now?

10
00:00:39,366 --> 00:00:40,400
We're supposed to
protect this area

11
00:00:40,433 --> 00:00:43,600
until the gate closes,
so let's focus on that first!

12
00:00:43,633 --> 00:00:44,766
[DDRAIG] Boost!

13
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:48,566
[SIR ZECHS] The only one

14
00:00:48,600 --> 00:00:51,033
who can use strong
protection magic is Rias.

15
00:00:54,266 --> 00:00:56,566
This whole thing's all my fault.

16
00:00:56,600 --> 00:00:57,766
[ISSEI] Rias!

17
00:00:59,700 --> 00:01:02,400
[GASPER] I should
help them. I wanna help.

18
00:01:02,633 --> 00:01:04,733
Rias! Issei!

19
00:01:05,466 --> 00:01:08,100
Please listen.
I can fight, too.

20
00:01:08,133 --> 00:01:10,266
I want to be a
man just like Issei is.

21
00:01:10,300 --> 00:01:12,100
I want to make
you all proud of me,

22
00:01:12,133 --> 00:01:13,766
and I want to be worthy of you.

23
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:16,300
I will fight. I just have to.

24
00:01:16,333 --> 00:01:19,366
I'm gonna do whatever it
takes to protect my friends!

25
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,633
You can't, Gasper!

26
00:01:20,666 --> 00:01:22,566
Please, Zechs,
you have to stop him!

27
00:01:22,600 --> 00:01:24,300
Do something!

28
00:01:24,333 --> 00:01:25,366
[GASPER] I can do this.

29
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:28,666
Watch me! I can be a man, too!

30
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:29,700
[RIAS] Gasper!

31
00:03:04,569 --> 00:03:05,936
Oh?

32
00:03:07,036 --> 00:03:08,269
What was that?

33
00:03:08,936 --> 00:03:10,469
Any idea what
just happened?

34
00:03:10,503 --> 00:03:11,569
I don't have a clue.

35
00:03:11,603 --> 00:03:12,969
Welcome back, Sona!

36
00:03:13,003 --> 00:03:14,636
Will you get off of me?

37
00:03:15,269 --> 00:03:16,603
Gasper did it.

38
00:03:16,636 --> 00:03:19,803
I'm not sure how, but he
made time go back to normal.

39
00:03:19,836 --> 00:03:21,803
[GRAYFIA] He stopped
the enemy gate, too.

40
00:03:21,836 --> 00:03:24,303
One less thing to
worry about, so hooray!

41
00:03:24,336 --> 00:03:25,736
Oh, hell yeah!

42
00:03:25,769 --> 00:03:27,736
You owned them, Gasper!

43
00:03:29,436 --> 00:03:30,869
I don't understand.

44
00:03:30,903 --> 00:03:32,869
We'll tell you
the details later.

45
00:03:32,903 --> 00:03:36,569
For now. I need everyone's help.

46
00:03:36,603 --> 00:03:38,203
[AKENO] You got it, Rias!

47
00:03:42,736 --> 00:03:44,336
Ring out, Thunder!

48
00:03:47,736 --> 00:03:48,636
Tsubaki!

49
00:03:48,669 --> 00:03:49,869
I'm on it, Sona.

50
00:03:53,336 --> 00:03:55,903
[AZAZEL] Well then, why don't
we start getting serious here?

51
00:03:55,936 --> 00:03:57,669
I'm so bored right now, are you?

52
00:03:57,703 --> 00:03:58,736
What're you holding?

53
00:03:58,769 --> 00:04:01,603
[AZAZEL] Something much
more interesting than war.

54
00:04:01,636 --> 00:04:03,669
Call it my hobby.

55
00:04:03,703 --> 00:04:05,969
This is the Downfall
Dragon Spear.

56
00:04:06,003 --> 00:04:09,636
It's an artificial Sacred Gear
developed by yours truly.

57
00:04:10,936 --> 00:04:12,969
[AZAZEL] Balance Break.

58
00:04:16,036 --> 00:04:17,503
What's he doing?

59
00:04:22,769 --> 00:04:24,903
[AZAZEL] Armor of
the Fallen Dragon.

60
00:04:24,936 --> 00:04:27,903
Downfall Dragon Another Armor.

61
00:04:27,936 --> 00:04:29,303
[ISSEI] A dragon's armor.

62
00:04:29,336 --> 00:04:31,569
He can do a
Balance Breaker, too?

63
00:04:33,336 --> 00:04:34,869
[AZAZEL] Now, come here.

64
00:04:34,903 --> 00:04:36,569
I'll kill you!

65
00:04:37,303 --> 00:04:39,503
[CATTLEYA screams]

66
00:04:39,536 --> 00:04:41,369
[AZAZEL]
Ha ha!

67
00:04:43,403 --> 00:04:44,736
[CATTLEYA] I am not
necessarily needed

68
00:04:44,769 --> 00:04:47,369
for the creation
of our new world!

69
00:04:47,603 --> 00:04:49,836
[CATTLEYA] If I can take out
one of the Three Great Powers,

70
00:04:49,869 --> 00:04:51,936
then I welcome death.

71
00:04:51,969 --> 00:04:54,269
[CATTLEYA] I'll destroy
myself for glory!

72
00:04:54,303 --> 00:04:56,369
[AZAZEL] Destroy yourself?
Ha!

73
00:04:56,403 --> 00:04:58,369
I don't want to mock
your hopes and dreams,

74
00:04:58,403 --> 00:05:00,403
but it doesn't seem worth it.

75
00:05:01,336 --> 00:05:03,369
[AZAZEL] You'll still die.

76
00:05:03,403 --> 00:05:05,669
[high-pitched wail]

77
00:05:06,869 --> 00:05:09,836
[AZAZEL] But I'm only willing
to give up an arm for you.

78
00:05:12,703 --> 00:05:13,869
And yet again
there's still plenty

79
00:05:13,903 --> 00:05:15,769
of room for improvement.

80
00:05:16,636 --> 00:05:17,569
But I guess you can stay

81
00:05:17,603 --> 00:05:19,469
with me a little while longer.

82
00:05:19,503 --> 00:05:22,003
My Dragon King Fafnir.

83
00:05:22,036 --> 00:05:23,636
That dude is hard.

84
00:05:23,669 --> 00:05:25,369
He lost his arm!

85
00:05:25,403 --> 00:05:26,736
We're not done.

86
00:05:26,769 --> 00:05:28,536
There are still a
few stragglers left.

87
00:05:28,569 --> 00:05:29,769
Right, yeah.

88
00:05:33,469 --> 00:05:34,369
Ascalon!

89
00:05:34,403 --> 00:05:35,703
[DDRAIG] Blade!

90
00:05:39,536 --> 00:05:41,869
Nice, they've
annihilated everyone.

91
00:05:45,669 --> 00:05:47,536
What the hell?

92
00:05:48,003 --> 00:05:48,803
Y'got me.

93
00:05:48,836 --> 00:05:51,803
Must be losing
my edge. Bad, Vali.

94
00:05:51,836 --> 00:05:53,403
[VALI] Sorry, Azazel.

95
00:05:53,436 --> 00:05:56,236
Things looked more
interesting on this side.

96
00:05:56,269 --> 00:05:57,436
[ISSEI] Vali!

97
00:05:57,469 --> 00:05:59,369
You're the one who betrayed us!

98
00:05:59,403 --> 00:06:00,336
I can understand,

99
00:06:00,369 --> 00:06:03,269
but there is something
I'd like to ask you.

100
00:06:03,303 --> 00:06:04,436
[VALI]
Hmm?

101
00:06:04,469 --> 00:06:06,736
[AZAZEL] You know Shemhaza,
my Vice Governor-General.

102
00:06:06,769 --> 00:06:08,469
Well, he's recently
informed me of a faction

103
00:06:08,503 --> 00:06:10,469
that has been gathering
the dangerous elements

104
00:06:10,503 --> 00:06:12,536
and members of the
Three Great Powers.

105
00:06:12,569 --> 00:06:14,336
What were they called?

106
00:06:14,369 --> 00:06:16,369
Oh, yes, the Chaos Brigade.

107
00:06:16,403 --> 00:06:17,936
Chaos sounds accurate.

108
00:06:17,969 --> 00:06:19,836
Whoever's in charge
must be strong.

109
00:06:19,869 --> 00:06:20,869
But why would
anyone gather

110
00:06:20,903 --> 00:06:22,936
such dangerous
people together?

111
00:06:22,969 --> 00:06:25,503
So. I bet I can guess
who's leading you.

112
00:06:25,536 --> 00:06:27,936
Has to be Orphis,
the Ouroboros Dragon, right?

113
00:06:27,969 --> 00:06:29,936
Orphis! It can't be!

114
00:06:29,969 --> 00:06:31,703
Is that another dragon?

115
00:06:31,736 --> 00:06:33,503
The Infinite Dragon God,

116
00:06:33,536 --> 00:06:36,669
a dragon so strong,
even God was afraid of him.

117
00:06:36,703 --> 00:06:39,469
[VALI] Yes, it is true
I have sided with Orphis.

118
00:06:39,503 --> 00:06:40,803
But believe me,
neither one of us

119
00:06:40,836 --> 00:06:43,903
has the slightest interest
in world domination.

120
00:06:44,903 --> 00:06:46,269
[VALI] We're just
a group who formed

121
00:06:46,303 --> 00:06:47,769
in order to use our power.

122
00:06:47,803 --> 00:06:48,836
And that's all.

123
00:06:48,869 --> 00:06:50,569
Well, that makes more sense.

124
00:06:50,603 --> 00:06:51,836
Conspiring with Cattleya seemed

125
00:06:51,869 --> 00:06:54,236
a little beneath you,
but even so.

126
00:06:54,269 --> 00:06:55,836
Both of you had
Devil Titles stolen,

127
00:06:55,869 --> 00:06:56,869
so I wasn't sure.

128
00:06:56,903 --> 00:06:58,503
He's a Devil King
descendant, too?

129
00:06:58,536 --> 00:06:59,536
What are you saying?

130
00:06:59,569 --> 00:07:01,769
[VALI] My name is Vali Lucifer.

131
00:07:01,803 --> 00:07:02,603
[SIR ZECHS] What?

132
00:07:02,636 --> 00:07:03,536
[ISSEI] Lucifer?

133
00:07:03,569 --> 00:07:04,803
[RIAS] No!

134
00:07:04,836 --> 00:07:07,769
[VALI] I am a direct descendant
of one of the dead Devil Kings.

135
00:07:07,803 --> 00:07:10,803
My mother was a human,
so I'm a half-blood.

136
00:07:10,836 --> 00:07:12,469
My father was
the grandson

137
00:07:12,503 --> 00:07:15,303
of the former
Great Devil King Lucifer.

138
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:30,867
[RIAS] No. It can't be true.

139
00:07:30,900 --> 00:07:33,300
[SIR ZECHS]
Of course. Half-human.

140
00:07:33,333 --> 00:07:35,600
There's no way we
could have known.

141
00:07:35,633 --> 00:07:38,867
[AZAZEL] While you have the
blood of a real Devil King,

142
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:41,300
since you are also a
human, you just happened

143
00:07:41,333 --> 00:07:44,100
to be able to be possessed
by the Vanishing Dragon.

144
00:07:46,100 --> 00:07:49,267
[AZAZEL] So basically,
your very existence is a joke.

145
00:07:49,300 --> 00:07:51,833
I would go with
"miracle" personally,

146
00:07:51,867 --> 00:07:53,633
but to each their own.

147
00:07:53,967 --> 00:07:55,700
[ASIA] Look at his wings!

148
00:07:56,933 --> 00:07:58,700
[MICHAEL] Dear God.

149
00:07:59,400 --> 00:08:00,567
[AZAZEL] I have a
feeling this one will be

150
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:04,767
the best White Dragon Emperor
the world has ever known.

151
00:08:04,800 --> 00:08:07,133
Past, present, and future.

152
00:08:07,167 --> 00:08:08,867
The best dragon ever.

153
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:12,833
[VALI] Issei Hyodo, fate can
be cruel, wouldn't you agree?

154
00:08:12,867 --> 00:08:14,333
Yeah. Maybe.

155
00:08:14,367 --> 00:08:16,300
[VALI] I am the
strongest dragon,

156
00:08:16,333 --> 00:08:19,933
and I carry with me the
blood of the Devil King.

157
00:08:19,967 --> 00:08:22,367
But you are just a lowly human.

158
00:08:22,400 --> 00:08:23,500
Before becoming a devil,

159
00:08:23,533 --> 00:08:26,800
you weren't even an impressive
student in high school.

160
00:08:26,833 --> 00:08:28,033
That is to say,

161
00:08:28,067 --> 00:08:32,200
aside from the Boosted Gear,
you are nothing.

162
00:08:32,233 --> 00:08:33,767
It's disappointing.

163
00:08:33,800 --> 00:08:36,133
It's so disappointing
it's funny.

164
00:08:36,167 --> 00:08:39,233
Even though we are
rival Sacred Gears--

165
00:08:39,267 --> 00:08:43,233
You and I are as far
apart as the sky to the earth.

166
00:08:43,267 --> 00:08:46,033
No, more than that.

167
00:08:46,067 --> 00:08:47,633
You got a point there, Vali?

168
00:08:47,667 --> 00:08:50,967
[VALI] I do; I think
you should try harder.

169
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,667
Maybe you should
try being an avenger.

170
00:08:53,700 --> 00:08:56,233
I could kill your parents
if that would help.

171
00:08:56,267 --> 00:08:58,000
[ISSEI] Eh?

172
00:08:58,933 --> 00:09:00,033
[VALI] If I take something,

173
00:09:00,067 --> 00:09:02,300
as precious to you as
your mother and father, away,

174
00:09:02,333 --> 00:09:05,867
surely you would be able
to act on that tragic fate.

175
00:09:05,900 --> 00:09:06,967
Your parents would most likely

176
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:09,367
be grateful to me
for their murder.

177
00:09:09,400 --> 00:09:10,433
Any death I would
grant them would be

178
00:09:10,467 --> 00:09:14,033
far more exciting than
their current boring life.

179
00:09:14,067 --> 00:09:15,733
Yes, let's do that.

180
00:09:15,767 --> 00:09:17,767
No. How can
he be so cruel?

181
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,700
Oh, Issei.

182
00:09:19,733 --> 00:09:21,733
I'm so gonna
kill this asshole.

183
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:23,767
[RIAS] Issei!

184
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,033
Why should my
parents have to die

185
00:09:25,067 --> 00:09:26,900
for his damn convenience?

186
00:09:26,933 --> 00:09:28,333
Like I would just sit idly by

187
00:09:28,367 --> 00:09:31,300
and let him take
anything from me!

188
00:09:32,867 --> 00:09:36,100
[DDRAIG]
Welsh Dragon Over Booster!

189
00:09:36,133 --> 00:09:38,067
[ISSEI] No one hurts
the people I care about.

190
00:09:38,100 --> 00:09:39,833
I don't care who they are!

191
00:09:39,867 --> 00:09:41,867
It's his Balance Breaker!

192
00:09:41,900 --> 00:09:43,133
[VALI] Look, Albion.

193
00:09:43,167 --> 00:09:45,967
The boy's power has
gone up exponentially.

194
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:48,733
[ALBION] The Sacred Gear
uses strong feelings

195
00:09:48,767 --> 00:09:50,633
to sustain its power.

196
00:09:50,667 --> 00:09:53,833
You're facing pure
rage from him right now.

197
00:09:53,867 --> 00:09:55,133
Well done.

198
00:09:55,167 --> 00:09:56,867
That is one of the
most appropriate ways

199
00:09:56,900 --> 00:09:59,100
of drawing out the dragon.

200
00:09:59,133 --> 00:10:01,100
[VALI] So what you're saying is,

201
00:10:01,133 --> 00:10:02,967
I'm even better at
drawing out his dragon

202
00:10:03,000 --> 00:10:04,633
than he is at being one.

203
00:10:04,667 --> 00:10:06,600
[ISSEI] Yeah, keep
talking, douchebag!

204
00:10:06,633 --> 00:10:08,633
Ascalon!

205
00:10:08,667 --> 00:10:09,767
[DDRAIG] Blade!

206
00:10:12,100 --> 00:10:13,133
[ALBION] The Dragon Slayer?

207
00:10:13,167 --> 00:10:16,800
I won't be able to deflect
even one cut from this.

208
00:10:16,833 --> 00:10:19,567
[VALI] All right, then
I won't let him cut me.

209
00:10:21,233 --> 00:10:22,833
Issei!

210
00:10:22,867 --> 00:10:24,667
Let me go; he needs me!

211
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:25,700
At this point,

212
00:10:25,733 --> 00:10:26,967
both of their auras
have passed their limits.

213
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,933
If you get too close to either
of them, you'll burn and die.

214
00:10:29,967 --> 00:10:33,167
But I-- I can't just
sit here and watch this!

215
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:35,333
[VALI] Weak. You're too weak!

216
00:10:35,867 --> 00:10:37,067
[splutters]

217
00:10:37,933 --> 00:10:39,900
[ALBION] Divide!

218
00:10:42,667 --> 00:10:45,633
[ISSEI] Damn it.
How could I have forgotten?

219
00:10:45,667 --> 00:10:47,000
He absorbs the power
of whatever comes

220
00:10:47,033 --> 00:10:49,033
into contact with his sword.

221
00:10:49,067 --> 00:10:50,133
I'm so stupid.

222
00:10:50,167 --> 00:10:51,667
[RIAS] Are you all right?

223
00:10:51,700 --> 00:10:55,900
[ISSEI] A-okay! You don't
have to worry about me!

224
00:10:55,933 --> 00:10:57,633
[GASPER] Issei, don't lose!

225
00:10:57,667 --> 00:10:59,100
You have to beat him!

226
00:10:59,133 --> 00:11:00,833
[ISSEI] I will.

227
00:11:00,867 --> 00:11:03,233
Especially since
Rias is watching!

228
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,933
[ISSEI] I won't
lose in front of her!

229
00:11:06,967 --> 00:11:08,200
[DDRAIG] Boost!

230
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:09,833
[VALI] Adorable.

231
00:11:09,867 --> 00:11:10,700
What did he do?

232
00:11:10,733 --> 00:11:12,367
[DDRAIG] He sent
the extra energy he got

233
00:11:12,400 --> 00:11:14,267
from you out through his wings.

234
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:15,767
By doing that,
he can maintain his power

235
00:11:15,800 --> 00:11:18,933
at the upper limits
of his capacity.

236
00:11:18,967 --> 00:11:20,933
[ISSEI] Okay, so no matter
how amazing he might be,

237
00:11:20,967 --> 00:11:23,267
there's still a limit
to what he can handle?

238
00:11:23,300 --> 00:11:24,800
[VALI] Exactly.

239
00:11:25,633 --> 00:11:26,867
[VALI] During the
fight with Kokabiel,

240
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:29,900
you were fighting for the sake
of your friends, weren't you?

241
00:11:29,933 --> 00:11:32,900
Does this mean
I should kill your friends,

242
00:11:32,933 --> 00:11:34,600
before I kill your family?

243
00:11:35,133 --> 00:11:37,700
[ISSEI] Asia!

244
00:11:37,733 --> 00:11:38,367
[VALI] What about her?

245
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,267
[ISSEI] You bastard!

246
00:11:39,300 --> 00:11:41,633
Stop fucking around,
you piece of shit!

247
00:11:41,667 --> 00:11:42,733
[VALI] Hate me more!

248
00:11:42,767 --> 00:11:43,867
Get angrier!

249
00:11:43,900 --> 00:11:46,067
Get stronger and
stronger for me.

250
00:11:46,100 --> 00:11:48,067
[VALI] Let's have some real fun.

251
00:11:49,267 --> 00:11:50,167
Issei, no!

252
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:53,067
[ISSEI] Ddraig!
Transfer power to Ascalon!

253
00:11:53,100 --> 00:11:54,900
