504
00:21:07,922 --> 00:21:08,989
[KONEKO] Don't worry.

505
00:21:09,022 --> 00:21:11,255
I promise nothing scary
will happen to you anymore.

506
00:21:11,289 --> 00:21:12,855
[GASPER] Finally, huh?

507
00:21:14,155 --> 00:21:15,522
[RIAS] Hey, Gasper.

508
00:21:15,555 --> 00:21:17,222
Oh. I'm sorry, Rias!

509
00:21:17,255 --> 00:21:19,189
This is-- this
was all my fault

510
00:21:19,222 --> 00:21:21,289
because the bad
guys wanted me.

511
00:21:21,322 --> 00:21:22,155
No, this was my fault

512
00:21:22,189 --> 00:21:24,289
because I failed to
protect you, Gaspie.

513
00:21:24,322 --> 00:21:26,189
You're wrong;
that's not true!

514
00:21:26,222 --> 00:21:27,022
Yes, it is true.

515
00:21:27,055 --> 00:21:29,522
[RIAS] You did
a good job, Koneko.

516
00:21:30,922 --> 00:21:32,689
You both did a good job.

517
00:21:32,722 --> 00:21:34,689
Gasper, I'm so proud of you.

518
00:21:34,722 --> 00:21:35,789
You were very brave just

519
00:21:35,822 --> 00:21:38,855
so you could help
the rest of us.

520
00:21:38,889 --> 00:21:40,822
And that makes me happy.

521
00:21:40,855 --> 00:21:44,522
I haven't been this
happy in such a long time.

522
00:21:44,555 --> 00:21:45,989
Yeah, me too.

523
00:21:46,022 --> 00:21:48,222
You made me really
happy, too, Gaspie.

524
00:21:48,255 --> 00:21:51,855
Oh, President Rias, and Koneko.

525
00:22:01,622 --> 00:22:03,522
[LEVIATHAN]
Sona. Confession time!

526
00:22:03,555 --> 00:22:05,822
I've taken a fancy to this
town and this high school.

527
00:22:05,855 --> 00:22:07,522
Oh, is that right?

528
00:22:09,789 --> 00:22:11,589
So, I'll come back soon!

529
00:22:15,655 --> 00:22:17,555
[SONA] No. Please don't do that.

530
00:22:17,589 --> 00:22:18,989
Please don't? Why?

531
00:22:19,022 --> 00:22:20,922
Um-- because
I uh-- said so.

532
00:22:20,955 --> 00:22:22,589
Hey Tsubaki,
you won't mind

533
00:22:22,622 --> 00:22:24,855
if I decide to come back
here again, will you?

534
00:22:24,889 --> 00:22:27,689
Uh-- I-- course not.

535
00:22:27,722 --> 00:22:28,855
[SONA] Tsubaki.

536
00:22:28,889 --> 00:22:30,889
But that's me.

537
00:22:30,922 --> 00:22:33,855
The president should be the
final judge of that, after all.

538
00:22:33,889 --> 00:22:35,655
[LEVIATHAN] No fair!

539
00:22:35,689 --> 00:22:37,022
[ISSEI] Chief Michael.

540
00:22:37,055 --> 00:22:39,989
Thank you very much
for granting my request.

541
00:22:40,022 --> 00:22:42,289
Let me know how I can repay you.

542
00:22:42,322 --> 00:22:43,722
But you already have.

543
00:22:43,755 --> 00:22:45,889
You performed a
distinguished service.

544
00:22:45,922 --> 00:22:47,522
Granting your request
doesn't even begin

545
00:22:47,555 --> 00:22:49,255
to compensate for what you did.

546
00:22:49,289 --> 00:22:51,789
[ISSEI] No sir,
that's not true at all.

547
00:22:52,622 --> 00:22:53,589
[XENOVIA thinking] I see.

548
00:22:53,622 --> 00:22:56,022
It's not because he has
the power of a Dragon.

549
00:22:56,055 --> 00:22:57,689
It's because he's a good man,

550
00:22:57,722 --> 00:23:01,889
the kind that attracts
people like Rias and Asia.

551
00:23:01,922 --> 00:23:03,622
And so, I must
return to Heaven

552
00:23:03,655 --> 00:23:06,689
to report on the
peace agreement.

553
00:23:06,722 --> 00:23:09,889
Next, we will work on measures
against the Chaos Brigade.

554
00:23:09,922 --> 00:23:11,155
Farewell.

555
00:23:14,789 --> 00:23:16,055
[ASIA] Issei.

556
00:23:16,955 --> 00:23:18,222
[ISSEI]
Isn't everything great, Asia?

557
00:23:18,255 --> 00:23:20,922
[ASIA] Oh, Issei. I love you!

558
00:23:22,955 --> 00:23:24,889
What did you
just say? Hey, Asia!

559
00:23:24,922 --> 00:23:26,955
Oh my goodness.

560
00:23:26,989 --> 00:23:29,922
Asia, I like how bold
you're getting to be.

561
00:23:31,222 --> 00:23:32,389
[SIR ZECHS] Well.

562
00:23:32,422 --> 00:23:34,555
I guess it was an important
factor after all, wasn't it?

563
00:23:34,589 --> 00:23:35,655
[GRAYFIA] What do you mean?

564
00:23:35,689 --> 00:23:37,155
[SIR ZECHS] Issei Hyodo.

565
00:23:37,189 --> 00:23:40,022
The true source of his power.

566
00:23:41,189 --> 00:23:42,289
[ISSEI] Xenovia!

567
00:23:42,322 --> 00:23:44,555
Now you can pray all you want!

568
00:23:44,589 --> 00:23:45,855
Isn't that awesome?

569
00:23:45,889 --> 00:23:48,689
Oh. Yeah. But um--

570
00:23:50,055 --> 00:23:53,922
No. I-- I
mean thank you.

571
00:23:56,089 --> 00:23:59,022
Now. Club
activities start tomorrow!

572
00:23:59,055 --> 00:24:01,089
[CLUB] You got it, Rias!

573
00:24:04,922 --> 00:24:08,255
[AZAZEL] And so, starting
from this day forward,

574
00:24:08,289 --> 00:24:11,789
I have become the advisor
for the Occult Research Club.

575
00:24:11,822 --> 00:24:13,689
Wait... you can't be serious.

576
00:24:13,722 --> 00:24:16,222
Oh, but I am; I asked
Sir Zechs and everything.

577
00:24:16,255 --> 00:24:17,055
He told me I should talk

578
00:24:17,089 --> 00:24:19,155
to Serafall's little
sister about it.

579
00:24:19,189 --> 00:24:20,522
[ISSEI] You did this, Sona?

580
00:24:20,555 --> 00:24:21,722
Look, I didn't
have much of a choice;

581
00:24:21,755 --> 00:24:24,289
if I didn't agree with it
my sister threatened the worst.

582
00:24:24,322 --> 00:24:26,022
She said she'd come instead.

583
00:24:26,055 --> 00:24:29,889
So basically, what you
mean is you sold us out.

584
00:24:29,922 --> 00:24:31,589
Anyway. I'll leave you to it.

585
00:24:31,622 --> 00:24:33,155
[RIAS] Hey, Sona!

586
00:24:33,855 --> 00:24:35,922
[ISSEI] Dude.
How'd you get that arm?

587
00:24:35,955 --> 00:24:38,589
Oh, my new friend here
is the omnipotent arm

588
00:24:38,622 --> 00:24:40,755
I made during all
my Sacred Gear research.

589
00:24:40,789 --> 00:24:42,789
I've always wanted to
equip something like this,

590
00:24:42,822 --> 00:24:44,922
and I'm so glad I did.

591
00:24:44,955 --> 00:24:48,655
Now, understand, Sir Zechs
had one condition for me.

592
00:24:48,689 --> 00:24:51,555
I cannot stay here unless
I provide a gift to you.

593
00:24:51,589 --> 00:24:53,755
[GASPER] Yeah?
What kind of gift?

594
00:24:53,789 --> 00:24:54,989
As long as I'm around,

595
00:24:55,022 --> 00:24:58,022
I will help you properly develop
your immature Sacred Gears.

596
00:24:58,055 --> 00:24:59,222
[chuckles]

597
00:24:59,255 --> 00:25:00,622
The mysterious Boosted Gear

598
00:25:00,655 --> 00:25:02,722
with unpredictable evolution.

599
00:25:02,755 --> 00:25:04,255
The Holy Devil Sword.

600
00:25:04,289 --> 00:25:06,055
And Forbidden Balor View.

601
00:25:07,589 --> 00:25:09,555
[AZAZEL] I can use the research
I've done to evolve them

602
00:25:09,589 --> 00:25:11,189
on an individual level,
understand?

603
00:25:11,222 --> 00:25:14,655
So, then, from now on you can
call me Mister Azazel, okay?

604
00:25:14,689 --> 00:25:17,255
Uh, "Mister Azazel"? Dude.

605
00:25:17,289 --> 00:25:19,722
Nothing personal, but that
feels weird in my mouth.

606
00:25:19,755 --> 00:25:21,955
I'm looking forward
to working with you all.

607
00:25:21,989 --> 00:25:23,589
Hold it; I never
agreed to this;

608
00:25:23,622 --> 00:25:24,255
how can we even trust you?

609
00:25:24,289 --> 00:25:25,389
[AZAZEL] Oh, yeah.

610
00:25:25,422 --> 00:25:28,089
Sir Zechs gave me another
message for you, as well.

611
00:25:28,122 --> 00:25:29,189
Another message?

612
00:25:29,222 --> 00:25:32,755
It seems when he stayed
at Issei's house previously,

613
00:25:32,789 --> 00:25:34,889
he learned the importance
of a good skinship

614
00:25:34,922 --> 00:25:36,555
between household members.

615
00:25:36,589 --> 00:25:37,955
Notably for you.

616
00:25:37,989 --> 00:25:39,655
Apparently that's what
the Red Dragon Emperor

617
00:25:39,689 --> 00:25:41,289
needs to charge his power.

618
00:25:41,322 --> 00:25:42,155
Okay.

619
00:25:42,189 --> 00:25:43,789
I don't get what
you're saying at all.

620
00:25:43,822 --> 00:25:44,789
[AZAZEL] All right, then.

621
00:25:44,822 --> 00:25:45,789
This is an official order

622
00:25:45,822 --> 00:25:47,889
in the name of the
great Devil King Lucifer.

623
00:25:47,922 --> 00:25:48,955
All of the
current female members

624
00:25:48,989 --> 00:25:51,822
of the Occult Research Club
are hereby directed

625
00:25:51,855 --> 00:25:53,989
to move in with
Issei immediately.

626
00:25:54,022 --> 00:25:54,922
There ya go.

627
00:25:54,955 --> 00:25:55,989
Move in?

628
00:25:56,022 --> 00:25:57,189
[AKENO] Issei.

629
00:25:57,222 --> 00:25:59,255
I'm here, and I swear
no matter what,

630
00:25:59,289 --> 00:26:01,189
I'll never leave your side!

631
00:26:01,222 --> 00:26:03,155
[ISSEI] Hey, cool, thanks!

632
00:26:03,189 --> 00:26:06,589
[XENOVIA] Should I just stay
in the same room as Asia then?

633
00:26:06,622 --> 00:26:09,622
Issei. I need to say something.

634
00:26:09,655 --> 00:26:10,189
Yeah?

635
00:26:10,222 --> 00:26:10,889
If you peek in my room,

636
00:26:10,922 --> 00:26:12,989
and steal or sniff my panties.

637
00:26:13,022 --> 00:26:14,822
I will make you suffer.

638
00:26:16,055 --> 00:26:16,989
This isn't fair.

639
00:26:17,022 --> 00:26:17,889
Yeah.

640
00:26:17,922 --> 00:26:19,255
I know, but my big
brother ordered it,

641
00:26:19,289 --> 00:26:21,955
so what can we do?

642
00:26:22,722 --> 00:26:24,622
I've got it!

643
00:26:24,655 --> 00:26:26,222
I'm going to demand
that my brother

644
00:26:26,255 --> 00:26:28,189
to remodel this
house completely!

645
00:26:28,222 --> 00:26:30,089
[ISSEI] You what?

646
00:26:34,989 --> 00:26:37,122
The White One is after power.

647
00:26:37,155 --> 00:26:40,022
And the Red is after women.

648
00:26:40,055 --> 00:26:42,022
Well, at least their
motives are pure,

649
00:26:42,055 --> 00:26:43,089
in their own way.

650
00:26:47,922 --> 00:26:48,522
[ISSEI] Hey!

651
00:26:48,555 --> 00:26:50,055
[AZAZEL] Even without God.

652
00:26:50,089 --> 00:26:52,189
The world keeps
right on turning.

